OL,3,CFamily remember 'bright and beautiful
OL,4,Cboy' who died in industrial park fire
OL,6,FThe family of a boy who died following
OL,7,Fa fire in Gateshead have said "he was
OL,8,Floved by all that met him, and it
OL,9,Fshowed".
OL,11,FLayton Carr's loved ones shared the
OL,12,Fheartfelt tribute on Monday (5 May),
OL,13,Fthree days after a fire at Fairfield
OL,14,FIndustrial Park, in the Bill Quay
OL,15,Farea, which claimed the 14-year-old's
OL,16,Flife.
