OL,3,CFamily remember 'bright and beautiful
OL,4,Cboy' who died in industrial park fire
OL,6,F16 children aged 11 to 14 were
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of manslaughter
OL,8,Fin connection with the incident and
OL,9,Fhave all been released on bail pending
OL,10,Ffurther enquiries.
OL,12,FIn a statement, his family said:
OL,13,F"Layton was such a kind, caring and
OL,14,Floving boy.
OL,16,F"From the minute he was born it was
OL,17,Fobvious the character he would turn
OL,18,Fout to be."
