OL,6,FThe family added: "Layton was your
OL,7,Ftypical 14-year-old lad, a cheeky,
OL,8,Fhappy lad. Despite his cheeky side
OL,9,FLayton had an absolute heart of gold
OL,10,Fand would do anything for anyone.
OL,12,F"He was loved by all that met him, and
OL,13,Fit showed.
OL,15,F"He was a family boy that loved his
OL,16,Fmam and sisters more than anything in
OL,17,Fthe world.
