OL,6,F"Layton, we love you more than any
OL,7,Fwords can ever explain. You will be
OL,8,Fmissed more than you'll ever know. Our
OL,9,Fbright and beautiful boy."
OL,11,FThey added: "As a family we would like
OL,12,Fto say a massive thank you to all that
OL,13,Fhelped in finding Layton.
OL,15,F"A massive thank you to the police and
OL,16,Fall services involved. We're
OL,17,Fincredibly grateful for the work that
OL,18,Fyou do every day to bring closure to
OL,19,Ffamilies like ours."
