OL,3,CFamily remember 'bright and beautiful
OL,4,Cboy' who died in industrial park fire
OL,6,FEleven boys and three girls aged
OL,7,Fbetween 11 and 14 were arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of manslaughter following
OL,9,Fthe incident on Friday evening (2 May).
OL,11,FA further two boys, aged 12, were
OL,12,Flater arrested on suspicion of
OL,13,Fmanslaughter.
OL,15,FThey have all since been released on
OL,16,Fpolice bail pending further enquiries.
OL,18,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,19,FJenkins, of Northumbria Police, said:
OL,20,F"Our thoughts remain with Layton's
OL,21,Ffamily at this devastating time.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
