OL,6,F"Our specialist officers will continue
OL,7,Fto support them in any way we can. We
OL,8,Fask that their privacy be respected at
OL,9,Fthis time.
OL,11,F"I would remind everyone not to
OL,12,Fspeculate on details of the incident
OL,13,Fonline or in the community ` what
OL,14,Fmight seem like a simple post on
OL,15,Fsocial media, could disrupt an on-
OL,16,Fgoing investigation.
OL,18,F"Circulation of malicious
OL,19,Fcommunications is classed as a
OL,20,Fcriminal offence and those who choose
OL,21,Fto be involved could face prosecution.
